{"id":1796,"date":"2018-05-10T09:40:23","date_gmt":"2018-05-10T09:40:23","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=1796"},"modified":"2021-02-27T08:44:29","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T08:44:29","slug":"vi-sao-nen-chon-go-cho-noi-gia-dinh","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/vi-sao-nen-chon-go-cho-noi-gia-dinh\/","title":{"rendered":"V\u00ec sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed3 g\u1ed7 cho n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t gia \u0111\u00ecnh?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">G\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang l\u1ea1i v\u1ebb sang tr\u1ecdng, t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, m\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 t\u1ee7 b\u1ebfp, gi\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7, b\u00e0n \u0103n, b\u00e0n tr\u00e0\u2026 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u g\u1ed7 c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i d\u00e1ng v\u1ebb g\u1ea7n g\u0169i, \u1ea5m \u00e1p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1738\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-3.jpg 960w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-3-300x103.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-3-768x264.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>V\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p sang tr\u1ecdng<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u n\u00e0o thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ed7 b\u1edfi v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p sang tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 b\u00e0n tr\u00e0, t\u1ee7 b\u1ebfp,&nbsp;gi\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7\u2026 b\u1eb1ng g\u1ed7 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n cho c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian trong nh\u00e0, h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa n\u00f3 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u00e0i h\u00f2a.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1710\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/32169233_1963557113678069_3015257669620465664_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"799\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/32169233_1963557113678069_3015257669620465664_n.jpg 960w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/32169233_1963557113678069_3015257669620465664_n-300x250.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/32169233_1963557113678069_3015257669620465664_n-768x639.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao c\u1ee7a g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00e0n c\u00e3i n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd v\u00e0 t\u1ea9m s\u1ea5y \u0111\u00fang quy c\u00e1ch. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i g\u1ed7 k\u00e9m b\u1ec1n. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p ng\u00e0y nay c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 c\u1ed1t g\u1ed7 MFC, finger&#8230; ch\u1ed1ng \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt, tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb m\u1ed1i m\u1ecdt, cong v\u00eanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft.&nbsp;G\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p&nbsp;c\u00f2n c\u00f3 lo\u1ea1i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng \u1ea9m, r\u1ea5t th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7t ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi hay nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 t\u1eafm, nh\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1751\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/36324391_2025753410791772_384269512792342528_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"521\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/36324391_2025753410791772_384269512792342528_n.jpg 960w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/36324391_2025753410791772_384269512792342528_n-300x163.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/36324391_2025753410791772_384269512792342528_n-768x417.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>S\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3 g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t v\u00e2n g\u1ed7, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e2n g\u1ed7 ho\u1eb7c m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp s\u01a1n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i hai lo\u1ea1i g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc gi\u1ed1ng h\u1ec7t nhau. V\u1edbi g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, hi\u1ec7n nay ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i c\u1ed1t g\u1ed7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho \u0111\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i c\u1ed1t g\u1ed7 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng cho nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf n\u01a1i kh\u00f4 r\u00e1o, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i c\u1ed1t g\u1ed7 ch\u1ed1ng \u1ea9m d\u00f9ng trong khu v\u1ef1c b\u1ebfp, nh\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh, ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi\u2026 C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1737\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-2.jpg 800w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-2-300x178.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-2-768x455.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Laminate: C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu l\u1ef1c cao c\u00f9ng v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tinh t\u1ebf, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u v\u00e2n g\u1ed7 kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Melamine: L\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc, \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1791\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/be-mat-melamin.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"609\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/be-mat-melamin.jpg 609w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/be-mat-melamin-300x147.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 609px) 100vw, 609px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Arcylic: Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt b\u1edfi v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p s\u00e1ng b\u00f3ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng lau ch\u00f9i, v\u1ec7 sinh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1731\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/may-dan-canh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/may-dan-canh-2.jpg 500w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/may-dan-canh-2-300x212.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Veneer: B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t Veneer l\u00e0 g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean l\u1ea1ng m\u1ecfng n\u00ean n\u00f3 mang v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1657\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/go-dan-venner.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/go-dan-venner.jpg 720w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/go-dan-venner-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/go-dan-venner-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/go-dan-venner-250x250.jpg 250w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>C\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1ea5m \u00e1p, g\u1ea7n g\u0169i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u l\u00e0m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t gia \u0111\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay r\u1ea5t phong ph\u00fa, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 nh\u1ef1a ch\u1ecbu l\u1ef1c ti\u1ec7n d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb, hay \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao nh\u01b0 inox, ngo\u00e0i ra c\u00f2n c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p kim xi m\u00e0u, composite&#8230; Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn cho kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ea1nh l\u1ebdo. Theo phong th\u1ee7y, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng lu\u1ed3ng kh\u00ed x\u1ea5u, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t b\u1eb1ng g\u1ed7 lu\u00f4n mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5m \u00e1p, gi\u00fap con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u00ecnh y\u00ean khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi m\u00e1i \u1ea5m gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1568\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/33535107_1978316035535510_9116493081363873792_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\"><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1564\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/33504542_1978315898868857_2488995739158446080_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u00edt d\u00f9ng g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 thay b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t Veneer th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1ng m\u1ecfng, b\u00ean trong l\u00e0 c\u1ed1t g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, v\u1eeba mang \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1588\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"563\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/5.jpg 563w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/5-300x220.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u chi ti\u1ebft r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0, kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a g\u1ed7 l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng duy\u00ean d\u00e1ng tr\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng. V\u00e0 b\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0103n bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n b\u00e8\u2026 ng\u1ed3i b\u00ean nhau khi ngo\u00e0i c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 m\u00e0n \u0111\u00eam d\u1ea7n bu\u00f4ng, m\u00f9i th\u1ee9c \u0103n th\u01a1m n\u1ee9c, ti\u1ebfng ly \u0111\u0169a lanh canh, ti\u1ebfng c\u01b0\u1eddi r\u00edu r\u00edt tr\u1ebb th\u01a1&#8230; b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn ra nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed3i \u0111\u1eafp t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected